data.description:
Back on the Market!
If you're looking for a home with a huge amount of potential, look no further! This charming log cabin nestled on a serene 1-acre lot in Freedom, WY is surrounded by beautiful trees and boasts a picturesque tributary of Salt River flowing through it. While the cabin does require some work, the bathroom and kitchen have been recently remodeled. The potential is undeniable, making it a perfect investment for short-term rentals, a vacation retreat, or even a perfect first-time home. Property has no restrictive covenants. (CC&R's). There are several outbuildings, a detached one-car garage, and an adorable guest cabin that dons an 1800's style woodstove. Property is being sold in as-is condition.
